  "text": "In previous studies addressing the value of anti-EGFR therapy in AGC, patients were not biomarker selected. However, in the EXPAND study a post-hoc analysis demonstrated no difference in survival according to EGFR immunohistochemistry score (with a median score of 0) [CITATION_1] . Similarly, in our post-hoc molecular ",
